<tmc-service-inc>
<pub id="RM21Q3EV">
<servcat id="33">
<name>TRANSMISSION</name>
<section id="1000S_S000F" variety="S000F">
<name>CLUTCH</name>
<ttl id="1000S_S000F_7A7ZJ_T003X" variety="T003X">
<name>CLUTCH MASTER CYLINDER</name>
<para id="RM000001FS901UX" category="A" type-id="80001" name-id="CL23N-01" from="201202">
<name>REMOVAL</name>
<subpara id="RM000001FS901UX_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000001FS901UX_01_0001" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000019500000">
<ptxt>DRAIN CLUTCH FLUID</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<atten3>
<ptxt>Wash off clutch fluid immediately if it comes into contact with a painted surface.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001FS901UX_01_0007" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00003A100000">
<ptxt>REMOVE LOWER INSTRUMENT CLUSTER FINISH PANEL
</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B291270" width="2.775699831in" height="2.775699831in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Detach the 7 claws and remove the lower instrument cluster finish panel.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1></s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001FS901UX_01_0008" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000053600000">
<ptxt>REMOVE COMBINATION METER ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="2">
<ptxt>(See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000004S68006X"/>)</ptxt>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001FS901UX_01_0004" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000019600000">
<ptxt>DISCONNECT CLUTCH RESERVOIR HOSE</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C192321" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using pliers, grip the claws of the clip and slide the clip, and then disconnect the clutch reservoir hose.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>Use a container to catch the fluid.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001FS901UX_01_0005" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000019700000">
<ptxt>DISCONNECT CLUTCH MASTER CYLINDER TO FLEXIBLE HOSE TUBE</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C192322E01" width="2.775699831in" height="2.775699831in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a union nut wrench, disconnect the tube.</ptxt>
<atten4>
<ptxt>Use a container to catch the fluid.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001FS901UX_01_0006" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000019800000">
<ptxt>REMOVE CLUTCH MASTER CYLINDER ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the clutch pedal (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000010R401VX"/>).</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the 2 nuts, clutch master cylinder assembly and gasket.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000001FS901UX_01_0009" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__000019A00000">
<ptxt>REMOVE CYLINDER PUSH ROD CLEVIS</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Loosen the lock nut, and then remove the clevis.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Remove the lock nut from the master cylinder.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
</servcat>
</pub>
